		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://werbach.com/wordpress/?p=1205</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[The FCC announced an order and consent decree fining a small local phone company for]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The FCC announced an <a href="http://hraunfoss.fcc.gov/edocs_public/attachmatch/DA-05-543A1.pdf">order </a> and consent decree fining a small local phone company for <a href="http://werbach.com/blog/archives/2005/02/why_we_need_net.html>blocking </a> the ports used by Vonage&#8217;s VOIP service.  It&#8217;s good to see the FCC taking quick action on Vonage&#8217;s complaint, and fulfilling Chairman Powell&#8217;s commitment to preserve &#8220;Net Neutrality&#8221; for broadband applications.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
